{"tid":1123872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有樓有高潮】Seasun成功翻撻趙世曾　獲贈豪宅慶生","createTime":"2019-04-24T17:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T11:56:30.000Z","uid":66271,"like":10,"dislike":289,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee3db3f223ed6de32228705b7c8d4cc97c173a2","tid":1123872,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2718384/org/79ecbe4f24e20eaed48d6635539a74e5.jpg/OJcO6_9PebM3c8EOKkN43fkWOceqyKUunOlUqpzpVKo?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2718384%2Forg%2F79ecbe4f24e20eaed48d6635539a74e5.jpg%2FOJcO6_9PebM3c8EOKkN43fkWOceqyKUunOlUqpzpVKo%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=64a0f8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於TVB真人騷《有樓萬事足》一句「有樓有高潮」轟動全城、被譽為港女典範的「高潮女」鄧湤鉮（Seasun）日前就風騷自爆獲緋聞男友，現年82歲富商趙世曾送她杭州價值過百萬的湖景樓盤做生日禮物，相當架勢！<br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的Seasun前年拍TVB真人騷《有樓萬事足》時爆出不少金句，包括「如果冇樓就唔好白撞。」、「有樓女人先有高潮。」和「要追我梗係要有誠意，準則就是要有一層樓，是表達愛的方法。」等，成功掀起全城話題。一夜成名的她被揭曾獲趙世曾安排她入住「趙苑」，但她突然帶男人返趙苑，最後被趙世曾趕走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2715709/org/4f1e8ba65cc8ec12eb61d3b79c3206c9.jpg/Ibvaf7SomcdylFJxnVCWO2X4aWGUhYZIyJJbsciSW7E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2715709%2Forg%2F4f1e8ba65cc8ec12eb61d3b79c3206c9.jpg%2FIbvaf7SomcdylFJxnVCWO2X4aWGUhYZIyJJbsciSW7E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e6bb61d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然Seasun因言論出位被圍插，但她年紀輕輕已經是業主，她在2017年以600萬買入筲箕灣300呎單位！她更獲導演青睞，接拍三級片《有罪》，當中有牀戲及裸露戲分。她最近更成功獲緋聞男友趙世曾「翻兜」，她接受《香港01》訪問時更直認：「下個月我要去杭州睇杭州湖邊的樓盤，到時影相拍片做記錄。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2715816/org/410f9b9522383c4a7a1e91268d2b9b3c.jpg/0d-K91x_QRgWn4V0uoI8YXOySQ4YXJeGlS6f1pUun9Y?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2715816%2Forg%2F410f9b9522383c4a7a1e91268d2b9b3c.jpg%2F0d-K91x_QRgWn4V0uoI8YXOySQ4YXJeGlS6f1pUun9Y%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ab27c2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n她更發了多張自己陪趙世曾覆診和入住對方位於薄扶林別墅的相片，看來生活過得非常富貴！至於問到感情生活，Seasun就以「#就算想都say no ，還想不想這行撈？」、「#我還是比較重情義的，也不想對不起對我有期望的人」回覆，相信意指自己為為保飯碗，暫時未敢拍拖！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2715809/org/d74589ba620845ddda1dd84a5c4233c7.jpg/dCz1Y22yqegwhX9DB4jTu50CYDoTM9K3JidY_yYnWP8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2715809%2Forg%2Fd74589ba620845ddda1dd84a5c4233c7.jpg%2FdCz1Y22yqegwhX9DB4jTu50CYDoTM9K3JidY_yYnWP8&h=4b80ee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2715808/org/7ce58e76c3f85abb9c3d5f9ea53a37c4.jpg/0KE4PDFVPUSE_EtU1NLRAUVP8r4s8x8RCt-IagrfiGo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2715808%2Forg%2F7ce58e76c3f85abb9c3d5f9ea53a37c4.jpg%2F0KE4PDFVPUSE_EtU1NLRAUVP8r4s8x8RCt-IagrfiGo&h=4c122929&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f0ac3dc17179dac25d72b2fe66cdbc67252a850","tid":1123872,"uid":592,"like":350,"dislike":3,"score":347,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:13:22.000Z","msg":"唔係話要港樓咩 <br />\n20m先襯得起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39a8af11a5ef35921c959b19623c70ef5f0e115","tid":1123872,"uid":61748,"like":7,"dislike":480,"score":-473,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:18:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1b57d558169f3ce8ec902340e6b332bf4e6f336","tid":1123872,"uid":194877,"like":501,"dislike":4,"score":497,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心佢啦 畀個呀伯屌<br />\n仲要話哂畀全世界知<br />\n佢畀人屌完有百幾萬既大陸危樓"},{"pid":"b8460f12355d52874acb79143eac8e2236ae34a5","tid":1123872,"uid":41818,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T17:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5afed1b6b199739ded5ea9b88c8f40e0b